Class WaitListReservation

  • java.lang.Object
    • hrps.entity.Reservation
      • hrps.entity.WaitListReservation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class WaitListReservation
extends Reservation
    This subclass represents pending reservations which are first created when a guest made a reservation and needed to be confirmed on check-in/check-out time and room number.
    Author:
    An Ruyi, Peng Wenxuan
